ocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 19, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zpr1665703006120.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zpr1665703006120.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zpr1665703006120.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zpr1665703006120\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__sleep_240021\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the current Uniface process in sleep mode for the specified amount of time.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__topic_d77354e1_d77355e1_d77356e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__p_d77357e1_d77358e1_d77359e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Ticks</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__section_w2218ab1b7b5_w2219ab1b7_w2220ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__p_d77360e1_d77361e1_d77362e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">sleep 500</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__topic_d50872e1_d50873e1_d50874e1_d50875e1_d50876e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1060926e77\">Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Ticks</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zpr1665703006120__table_d7436e1_d7437e1_d7438e1__entry__3\">\n Time period, specified in hundredths of a second. There is no default value; must be a positive integer.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__topic_d50877e1_d50878e1_d50879e1_d50880e1_d50881e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1060926e131\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__topic_d50882e1_d50883e1_d50884e1_d50885e1_d50886e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1060926e141\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__topic_d50887e1_d50888e1_d50889e1_d50890e1_d50891e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1060926e150\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__p_d77381e1_d77382e1_d77383e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span> ProcScript statement requests the current Uniface application to pause execution for approximately the specified period of time. The actual clock time blocked is dependent on the underlying operating system.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__note_w2221ab1b7c13b5_w2222ab1b7c13_w2223ab1b7_w2224ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span> is guaranteed to block for at least the requested time, but,\n            depending on the operating system, the actual blocking time could be longer, because not\n            all systems support time resolution in ticks.</div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zpr1665703006120__note_w2225ab1b7c13b7_w2226ab1b7c13_w2227ab1b7_w2228ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> On Microsoft Windows, while a process is blocked using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span>, the screen is not repainted, which could result in parts of\n            the application screen going blank until the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span> finishes. When you\n            wish to use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span> for more than a few seconds, consider using\n            multiple <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sleep</span> commands, or putting them in a loop, so the screen can\n            be repainted in between.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534556\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534556\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "sleep Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 19, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the current Uniface process in sleep mode for the specified amount of time. sleep Ticks Example: sleep 500 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Ticks Number Time period, specified in hundredths of a second. There is no default value; must be a positive integer. Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description The sleep ProcScript statement requests the current Uniface application to pause execution for approximately the specified period of time. The actual clock time blocked is dependent on the underlying operating system. CAUTION: sleep is guaranteed to block for at least the requested time, but, depending on the operating system, the actual blocking time could be longer, because not all systems support time resolution in ticks. Note: On Microsoft Windows, while a process is blocked using sleep , the screen is not repainted, which could result in parts of the application screen going blank until the sleep finishes. When you wish to use sleep for more than a few seconds, consider using multiple sleep commands, or putting them in a loop, so the screen can be repainted in between. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}